Some APIs to use as examples/tests:

[Google+](https://developers.google.com/+/api/)
[Last.fm](http://www.last.fm/api/intro)
[Imgur](http://api.imgur.com/)


The markdown files could be shared as "recipes" ala Homebrew.

Easy to express the recipes as JSON, too. Whether with the request and
responses in their pre-parsed form, or post-parsed form, or both.
